text: West End is an unincorporated community in Franklin and Saline counties in the U.S. state of Illinois. The portion of the community in Franklin County is part of Cave Township, while the portion in Saline County is part of Tate Township. The community is located along Illinois Route 34 east-southeast of Thompsonville. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Franklin County, Illinois Category:Unincorporated communities in Saline County, Illinois Category:Unincorporated communities in Illinois
